GITS Server Documentation
-------------------------
!!!Not realy a documentation yet!!!
Yust a collection of ideas to help me going.

_Input:_
	somthing like this:
	([Char],Integer,[Char],(Integer,Integer,Integer),[Char])
	What does what:
	(<command>,Event ID,<Event Name>,<Day,Hour,Minute>,<Room>) 
	
	commands:
		com: commit an event to the server
		del delete an entry
		chanN: change Name
		chanT: change Time
		chanR: change Room

_output:_
	a list of all we need:
	[(Int,[Char],(Int,Int,Int),[Char])]
	Function:
	[(Event Id, <Event Name>, <Day,Hour,Minute>, Roomname)]

	IRC Anouncments?

_Interna_
	How to save this? Database? File?

	Should the client order the times or the server?
	I Guess the server since we have to check for time overlapping
	per room. 

__Config File Format__
The Config File is Basicle a of the Format:
(Key, Value)
(Key, Value)
...

unse CfgParse to get values.
The function parser:: String -> String -> String will do niceley
Usage:	     parser  <Key> <IO String>

_Passwd.cnf_
The passwd.cnf is in the format:
(User,Pass);[Priveleg1,Priveleg2, ... Priveleg n]

Priveleges are:
Update: Can get a fresh Copy of the Fahrplan
Edit: Can Edit Single Entrys 
All: All of the Above
